CVE-2025-41249: Fix annotation detection with unresolved generics in type hierarchies

Spring Framework failed to detect method-level security annotations on methods
declared in generic superclasses or interfaces with unbounded type parameters.
ResolvableType.resolve() returns null for unresolved generics, preventing
override detection. Using ResolvableType.toClass() (which falls back to
Object.class) restores correct annotation inheritance.

Origin: upstream, https://github.com/spring-projects/spring-framework/commit/6d710d482a6785b069e35022e81758953afc21ff
Bug: CVE-2025-41249

